
Add the feature of upsrteam health check for upstream fair module in Tengine

$ git clone git://github.com/gnosek/nginx-upstream-fair.git
$ cd nginx-upstream-fair
$ patch -p1 < /path/to/this/upstream-fair-upstream-check.patch
$ cd /path/to/tengine
$ ./configure --with-http_upstream_check_module --add-module=/path/to/nginx-upstream-fair
$ make
$ make install
